# Welcome to CodeOnly

CodeOnly is a simple, lightweight, easy-to-learn framework for
front-end web development, designed for coders.


Use the menu at the left (or top-left on mobile) to learn more.

```js
// demo
// Components extend the `Component` class
class Main extends Component
{
    // Public variable are available in the template
    count = 0;

    // As are event handlers
    onClick() 
    { 
        // Increment counter
        this.count++; 

        // Mark DOM as needing to be updated
        this.invalidate(); 
    }

    // This is the component's template
    static template = {

        // The element type
        type: "button",

        // The element's text content.
        // By declaring this as a callback function we
        // can dynamically update it by "invalidating"
        // the component
        text: c => `Click Me: ${c.count}`,

        // Click handler
        on_click: c => c.onClick(),

    }
}
```